&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO WE ARE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Vox Media Podcast Network is one of the largest U.S. podcast publishers, home to some of the most popular and influential shows. Reaching a monthly audience of tens of millions across audio, video, and social platforms, our podcasts spark conversations and shape culture, covering everything from politics, technology, and business to food, lifestyle, sports, entertainment, and more. The Vox Media Podcast Network is powered by Vox Media, the leader in modern media, and home to a prestigious portfolio of editorial brands including New York Magazine, Vox, The Verge, Eater, SB Nation, and more. Learn more at podcasts.voxmedia.com.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Director of Podcast Partnerships, you will be a driven revenue contributor responsible for growing relationships with CPG and Retail brands and developing new business across the Vox Media Podcast Network. You will serve as a strategic partner to brand marketers and agencies, delivering innovative podcast and talent solutions that connect brands with highly engaged, intellectually curious audiences at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leveraging Vox Media&#39;s premium podcast network — including leading shows and high-profile talent across food, lifestyle, culture, sports, and entertainment — high-value audiences, and unique scale, you will build partnerships that drive measurable brand outcomes. This role demands a consultative mindset, strong relationship-building skills, a passion for podcasts and talent, and a relentless drive to grow revenue in a fast-paced, ambitious environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive CPG &amp;amp; Retail Revenue Growth:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and manage a growing book of business with CPG and Retail clients, identifying opportunities to deepen existing partnerships and win new ones across the Vox Media Podcast Network.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Key Relationships:&lt;/strong&gt; Cultivate strong relationships with brand managers, VP and SVP-level marketing decision-makers, and agency partners — positioning Vox Media as a trusted, go-to partner for podcast and talent investment in the CPG and Retail categories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proactive Market Engagement:&lt;/strong&gt; Stay ahead of industry trends, seasonal planning cycles, and shifting shopper behaviors, bringing forward-looking podcast and talent solutions to clients before RFPs are issued.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultative Selling:&lt;/strong&gt; Translate CPG and Retail client objectives — brand awareness, product launches, seasonal campaigns, and shopper intent — into high-impact campaigns using Vox Media podcasts, host talent, video, social, and live event capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Category Fluency:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage and expand working expertise in the CPG and Retail advertising landscape, contributing insights that help shape sales strategy and strengthen client proposals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Revenue Accountability:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage your pipeline with rigor, maintain accurate forecasting, and consistently deliver against quarterly and annual revenue targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with editorial, marketing, creative, production, and operations teams to develop culturally resonant proposals that speak directly to how CPG and Retail brands connect with consumers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brand Representation: &lt;/strong&gt;Represent the Vox Media Podcast Network at relevant industry events, CPG and Retail conferences, and client meetings to grow our presence within those communities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO YOU ARE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experienced Media Sales Talent:&lt;/strong&gt; 5+ years of digital media

