&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in podcast production, audio journalism, or editorial news leadership, with a demonstrated track record managing high-output, fast-paced editorial operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience leading and developing editorial teams, including direct management of producers and editors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong news judgment and deep familiarity with the political, tech, and culture landscapes that define On with Kara Swisher&#39;s editorial identity&lt;/li&gt;
