&lt;p&gt;This role carries full strategic ownership of a series of categories for UK and global accounts with accountability for individual revenue performance, market positioning, and long-term growth.&amp;nbsp; The ideal candidate will utilise their expertise and knowledge to unlock the full potential of the assigned categories by providing clients with a unique blend of premier content offerings, high-value audiences and cutting- edge innovations across a deep brand portfolio of publishing and podcast offerings.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
