&lt;p&gt;This is a high-energy and high-volume role that requires persistent and persuasive interactions with clients, deep digital, social and audio expertise, proven sales skills and the ability to work independently and collaboratively with clients and internal teams to close deals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This is a 12 month temporary engagement to provide parental leave coverage.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
